# Test and dev files
# Note: page-objects/ and test-utils/ are intentionally NOT excluded.
# Production components (e.g. CreateInstanceModal, AuditLogs, Logs) import
# dataTestIds/pageElements constants from page-objects/constants/..., so
# these paths cannot be excluded from the build context.
